# Core Tokenizer

Files in submission
---
README - this file, including instructions on how to run the program
DOCUMENTATION - contains description of the Tokenizer class design, a user manual, and description of testing
tokenizer.py - source file containing code behind the tokenizer class implementation in Python3

How to run
---
python3 tokenizer.py [test.core]

Source code is passed in as a CLI arg. Usage information will print if a file is not provided, and an error will show if an invalid file is provided.
Development/testing was completed on Ubuntu, but it only uses the sys package so it should work on any OS without issue.